Significant Achievements
Debut & First Win: Made his debut in 2007 and achieved his first win at the 2008 Italian Grand Prix, becoming the youngest-ever F1 winner.
Podiums: Secured 122 podium finishes during his career.
Pole Positions: Achieved 57 pole positions, ranking among the best in F1 history.
Legacy: Known for his speed on track and off-track advocacy for environmental and social causes in his final years. 
